{"author":{"id":"02ecfeec5e3d9ae3fcb4ee7636634148fee4f97bfc8cfa132041bf8882dd22ae"},"ops":[{"type":3,"timestamp":1437767949,"nonce":"ojABxRsCVZRZGBZAuhGpAxARI+Q=","metadata":{"github-id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDEyNDY5MDczNQ==","github-url":"https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/issues/221#issuecomment-124690735"},"message":"I’ve found that in some cases I’ve needed the following chang to the package_atlas_3_10 recipe.  I have not submitted a pull request for the patch because I’m still in the process of ironing out my recipes and (until now) I was not aware of anyone else bumping into this issue, so I figured it may just be “me doing something wrong”. \n\ndiff --git a/packages/package_atlas_3_10/tool_dependencies.xml b/packages/package_atlas_3_10/tool_dependencies.xml\nindex e1cb3cd..8069c7e 100644\n--- a/packages/package_atlas_3_10/tool_dependencies.xml\n+++ b/packages/package_atlas_3_10/tool_dependencies.xml\n@@ -8,6 +8,9 @@\n                         \u003csource_directory\u003e.\u003c/source_directory\u003e\n                         \u003cdestination_directory\u003e$INSTALL_DIR\u003c/destination_directory\u003e\n                     \u003c/action\u003e\n-                    \u003caction type=\"shell_command\"\u003e\n-                        export ATLAS_LIB_DIR=$INSTALL_DIR/lib\n-                    \u003c/action\u003e\n                   \u003caction type=\"set_environment\"\u003e\n                       \u003cenvironment_variable action=\"set_to\" name=\"ATLAS_LIB_DIR\"\u003e$INSTALL_DIR/lib\u003c/environment_variable\u003e\n                       \u003cenvironment_variable action=\"set_to\" name=\"ATLAS_INCLUDE_DIR\"\u003e$INSTALL_DIR/include\u003c/environment_variable\u003e\n  @@ -44,6 +47,7 @@\n                   \u003caction type=\"shell_command\"\u003etar -jxvf atlas3.10.2.tar.bz2\u003c/action\u003e\n                   \u003c!-- a 64-bit architecture is assumed for compilation --\u003e\n                   \u003caction type=\"shell_command\"\u003e\u003c![CDATA[\n-                        export ATLAS_LIB_DIR=$INSTALL_DIR/lib \u0026\u0026\n                       cd ATLAS \u0026\u0026\n                       mkdir ATLAS/build \u0026\u0026\n                       patch -p1 \u003c/host/static_full_blas_lapack.diff \u0026\u0026\n\nThe tool_dependencies.xl file for pacage_htseq_count_0_6 at https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/tree/master/packages/package_htseq_0_6 https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/tree/master/packages/package_htseq_0_6 contains this:\n\n```\n            \u003caction type=\"set_environment_for_install\"\u003e\n                \u003crepository name=\"package_numpy_1_7\" owner=\"iuc\"\u003e\n                    \u003cpackage name=\"numpy\" version=\"1.7.1\" /\u003e\n                \u003c/repository\u003e\n```\n\nAnd the tool_dependencies.xml file for package_numpy_1_7 available at  https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/blob/master/packages/package_numpy_1_7/tool_dependencies.xml https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/blob/master/packages/package_numpy_1_7/tool_dependencies.xml contains this:\n\n```\n    \u003cpackage name=\"atlas\" version=\"3.10.2\"\u003e\n        \u003crepository name=\"package_atlas_3_10\" owner=\"iuc\" prior_installation_required=\"True\" /\u003e\n    \u003c/package\u003e\n```\n\nand this:\n\n```\n        \u003caction type=\"shell_command\"\u003e\n          cat \u0026gt; site.cfg \u0026lt;\u0026lt;EOF\n```\n\n[DEFAULT]\nlibrary_dirs = $ATLAS_LIB_DIR\ninclude_dirs = $ATLAS_INCLUDE_DIR\n[blas_opt]\nlibraries = blas, atlas\n[lapack_opt]\nlibraries = lapack, atlas\nEOF\n            \u003c/action\u003e\n\nSo could these packages as well as some others require the above patch to the atlas package as well?\n\n\u003e On Jul 24, 2015, at 3:47 PM, Björn Grüning notifications@github.com wrote:\n\u003e \n\u003e @lparsons https://github.com/lparsons can you check if this solves your problem. https://github.com/galaxyproject/galaxy/pull/403/files https://github.com/galaxyproject/galaxy/pull/403/files\n\u003e It took us a while to track this down, but at least for me it fixes this issue.\n\u003e \n\u003e —\n\u003e Reply to this email directly or view it on GitHub https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/issues/221#issuecomment-124679105.","files":null}]}